I"^<h1 id="openproject-426">OpenProject 4.2.6</h1>

<p>OpenProject 4.2.6 contains a bug fixes and updated translations.</p>

<p>The following bugs have been fixed:</p>

<ul>
  <li>In projects with a lot of (potential) watchers an error occurred
when changing the work package type while creating a work package.
This error has been fixed
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/21233">#21233</a>).</li>
  <li>Occasionally, a wrong language was displayed in the work package
split screen. This has been fixed
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/21219">#21219</a>).</li>
  <li>An error has been fixed which prevented user creation with
authentication via LDAP
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/21129">#21129</a>).</li>
  <li>Several wrong English strings have been fixed
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/21240">#21240</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/21248">#21248</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/21253">#21253</a>).</li>
</ul>

<p>Additionally, OpenProject 4.2.6 containsÂ new translations.</p>

<p>For further information on the release, please refer to the <a href="https://community.openproject.org/versions/762">Changelog
v.4.2.6</a> or take a look
at <a href="https://github.com/opf/openproject/tree/v4.2.6">GitHub</a>.</p>

